1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,060
= Episode 49 =

20
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:36,620
During the painting for a dozen days,

21
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:38,340
Cui Bai had a crush on me.

22
00:01:39,620 --> 00:01:40,980
Because of his painting,

23
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:43,100
I adored him, too.

24
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:46,820
He expressed his love with a painting,

25
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:48,020
and I accepted him.

26
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:50,460
I promised to marry him

27
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:52,060
after I left the palace.

28
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,260
I swear.

29
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:57,900
I don’t dare to conceal the truth.

30
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,700
I pledged to marry him without permission.

31
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:02,420
I broke the imperial rule.

32
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,500
But we’ve been courteous

33
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:06,100
and we never have inappropriate intimacy

34
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:10,260
I...

35
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,940
I’d like to have the Imperial Recorder

36
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:16,140
check my virginity.

37
00:02:17,820 --> 00:02:19,380
You tell me this,

38
00:02:20,700 --> 00:02:22,260
because you want me to keep my promise,

39
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:24,580
to let you leave the palace

40
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:25,940
instead of punishing you?

41
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:27,340
No.

42
00:02:27,620 --> 00:02:29,700
Your Majesty, I tell you this,

43
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:32,020
because I believe you’ll judge it wisely

44
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:34,420
after you know what really happened

45
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,980
and you won’t let others

46
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:37,940
make groundless accusations

47
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:39,860
or blame anyone wrongly.

48
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:43,700
I broke the imperial rule

49
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:45,300
and I should be punished.

50
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:46,780
I won’t complain about that.

51
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,980
Then why do you come

52
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:54,900
and ask me to keep my promise?

53
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:59,660
Your Majesty, it took you more than one hour

54
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:02,340
to listen to my

55
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:03,940
story.

56
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:06,380
This is exactly what I want.

57
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:09,620
As for the investigation and judgement,

58
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,460
I’m afraid too many rules or laws

59
00:03:13,180 --> 00:03:14,260
are involved,

60
00:03:15,260 --> 00:03:17,300
I don’t dare to coerce you

61
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:18,580
with an old promise.

62
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:24,300
Thank you, Your Majesty,

63
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:25,580
for keeping your promise.

64
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:31,860
You come to confess to me,

65
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:34,220
regardless of your own punishment.

66
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:38,700
Do you fear to put Cui Bai into trouble

67
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:40,820
or to get the Empress involved?

68
00:03:41,740 --> 00:03:42,540
However,

69
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:44,860
don’t you fear

70
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,620
it’ll confirm that Cui Bai is unrestrained

71
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:48,380
and the Empress isn’t strict with her maids,

72
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:51,100
and even wants to draw officials over

73
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:52,540
with her maids?

74
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:56,100
I just fear you don’t know the truth.

75
00:03:57,820 --> 00:03:59,260
Since you know,

76
00:03:59,700 --> 00:04:00,580
I won’t complain,

77
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,660
however hard you punish me.

78
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:03,460
And I believe.

79
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:05,180
Since you know the truth,

80
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:07,300
you’ll vindicate Her Highness.

81
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,980
Seems like you trust me

82
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:17,100
more than the Empress does.

83
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:22,140
Her Highness loves you.

84
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,220
So, she’s anxious.

85
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,060
When closely involved,

86
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:27,660
she can’t see clearly.

87
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:37,540
Well, look at you.

88
00:04:37,540 --> 00:04:38,820
You’re an interesting girl.

89
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:40,860
No wonder she likes you.

90
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:42,980
Fine.

91
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,540
Since you’re frank,

92
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:47,860
let me tell you the truth, too.

93
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:50,780
Recently, people are talking about

94
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:53,300
what happened between you and Cui Bai.

95
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:55,100
Some said

96
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:58,460
everyone involved must be checked carefully.

97
00:04:58,700 --> 00:05:01,300
Some even wanted to imprison you.

98
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,540
But...

99
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,180
I wasn’t going to

100
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,260
investigate on it.

101
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,700
After you explained to me,

102
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:12,220
I’m sure about it now.

103
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:15,700
You know what?

104
00:05:17,780 --> 00:05:19,260
I remember the Empress told me that

105
00:05:19,660 --> 00:05:22,620
some maids would leave in a few days.

106
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:27,260
You’re one of them, I guess.

107
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:30,620
Yes.

108
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:33,500
But I’ve decided to

109
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,140
beg Her Highness to let me stay with her

110
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:36,220
instead of leaving the palace.

111
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:39,300
Since people are talking about it,

112
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:40,900
if I leave at this moment,

113
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,580
someone will track me down.

114
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,700
I don’t...

115
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,620
I don’t want to get Cui Bai involved.

116
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:50,180
Besides,

117
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:52,820
I don’t want to leave Her Highness.

118
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:56,020
I’d like to stay with her for the rest of my life

119
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,500
and take care of her.

120
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:03,700
I’m even jealous of

121
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:06,180
your loyalty to her.

122
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,700
I keep making trouble for Her Highness

123
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:10,980
all the time.

124
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:12,540
I’m sorry to her.

125
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,940
Instead of blaming me,

126
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:17,700
she always helps me.

127
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,540
I think

128
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,460
in the palace,

129
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:25,460
I can continue to

130
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:26,940
make crowns and hairpins,

131
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:28,980
and stay with Her Highness,

132
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:30,580
learning from her.

133
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,500
It’s my luck.

134
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:49,340
Your Majesty.

135
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:52,660
Her Highness must be considerate

136
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:53,740
and remain graceful

137
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:56,500
so that people will respect her.

138
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:58,340
She can let nothing go wrong.

139
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:00,460
But in fact,

140
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:03,780
she has passions

141
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,500
and she can be weak, too.

142
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:08,020
However,

143
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:09,860
she can’t tell her families

144
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:11,140
about her grievances.

145
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:13,380
Nor can she tell her husband.

146
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:16,060
To her husband,

147
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:17,980
she’s not only a wife,

148
00:07:17,980 --> 00:07:19,020
but also a subordinate.

149
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:23,180
She thinks she must work for Your Majesty.

150
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:25,180
She doesn’t dare to bother you.

151
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:30,540
On the day of coup,

152
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:32,540
she didn’t want to

153
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:34,060
die with you.

154
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:37,660
She would only die alone to protect you.

155
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:40,020
She took herself

156
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:41,620
as your subordinate.

157
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:44,740
Madam Zhang disobeyed the rule

158
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:46,020
and get out of her chamber.

159
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:48,540
Instead of punishing her,

160
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:50,700
you comforted her gently.

161
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:53,340
You spoiled her, regardless of right or wrong.

162
00:07:57,900 --> 00:07:58,620
Your Majesty.

163
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:01,060
When Her Highness saw that,

164
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:04,220
she was sad and aggrieved.

165
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:06,180
Could she...

166
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:09,340
Could she believe that

167
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:10,340
you would handle this problem

168
00:08:10,540 --> 00:08:11,940
in a fair way?

169
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:22,260
She punished Ling’er,

170
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,460
according to the rule,

171
00:08:24,700 --> 00:08:26,660
and in this way,

172
00:08:26,740 --> 00:08:28,260
no one could use Ling’er for more accusations.

173
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,260
But in my heart,

174
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,140
I’ve got a better plan.

175
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:36,380
I hate her for not trusting me.

176
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,580
But you’re right.

177
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:41,580
I’ve been so bad to her

178
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:43,540
over so many years.

179
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,580
How can she trust me

180
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,540
with her whole heart?

181
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,420
Your Majesty.

182
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,660
Her Highness is very lonely.

183
00:08:56,220 --> 00:08:57,460
I’m begging you.

184
00:08:58,300 --> 00:09:00,860
Let me stay with her all my life.

185
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:07,460
Okay.

186
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:09,860
I promise you.

187
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:16,140
Stand up.

188
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:25,860
Go to Imperial Office Bureau,

189
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:27,860
and take a message to Zhang Maoze.

190
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:30,220
He did hard work

191
00:09:30,940 --> 00:09:31,940
for days.

192
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,180
Ask Liaozi to go with you.

193
00:09:37,300 --> 00:09:38,260
Take the case

194
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,620
to him.

195
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:43,580
And...

196
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:46,740
ask the Empress to bring me

197
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:48,340
two jars of peach wine.

198
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:52,980
I didn’t enjoy it last time.

199
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:16,100
Mr. Zhang.

200
00:10:16,940 --> 00:10:17,980
I know you do everything,

201
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,580
for His Majesty and Her Highness

202
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:21,820
and you don’t like what Madam Zhang does.

203
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,220
But...

204
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:24,140
Do know

205
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:29,620
how the former empress

206
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:31,420
Madam Guo died?

207
00:10:32,913 --> 00:10:33,743
Wasn’t...

208
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:37,580
Wasn’t she dead

209
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:39,580
in her self-cultivation?

210
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:42,300
His Majesty didn’t like Madam Guo.

211
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,660
But he didn’t want her to live alone,

212
00:10:44,660 --> 00:10:45,740
and wanted to get her back.

213
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:48,700
Yan Wenying helped most

214
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:50,340
in dethroning her.

215
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:52,980
For fear that Madam Guo might come back

216
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:54,140
and take revenge,

217
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:56,740
he took physicians to cure her

218
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:59,460
when she had a cold.

219
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:02,700
Then, she was sicker.

220
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:06,340
She was poisoned?

221
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:09,300
No.

222
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:13,300
She was buried alive.

223
00:11:18,140 --> 00:11:19,860
Yan Wenying didn’t dare to

224
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:20,860
poison Madam Guo.

225
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:23,180
That would be obvious.

226
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:25,900
He just changed the prescription

227
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,260
and made her sicker.

228
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:29,180
By then,

229
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,540
His Majesty was coming back

230
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:32,860
from the fast in southern suburbs.

231
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:35,500
In case that His Majesty visited Madam Guo

232
00:11:37,260 --> 00:11:38,460
after he came back,

233
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:43,500
Yan Wenying put her

234
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:46,260
in the coffin

235
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,100
before she was dead.

236
00:12:00,740 --> 00:12:01,340
I...

237
00:12:04,220 --> 00:12:05,660
I won’t let Her Highness

238
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,820
suffer the same thing.

239
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:12,940
But...

240
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:14,020
But His Majesty...

241
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:17,300
His Majesty cares for Her Highness.

242
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:18,100
I know.

243
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:23,820
But His Majesty cares for

244
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:25,140
so many people and things.

245
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:27,780
He may not take care of them all.

246
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:32,820
He only wants a balance

247
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:39,180
between the imperial court and imperial harem.

248
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:42,900
But you’re doing this.

249
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:47,620
His Majesty has warned you.

250
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:30,260
I’m investigating by myself.

251
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:37,660
No one asked me to.

252
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:53,540
His Majesty is wise.

253
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:55,460
He certainly knows.

254
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:58,700
He won’t blame others

255
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:01,140
because he is unsatisfied with me.

256
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:05,100
As for myself,

257
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:12,340
I won’t complain

258
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:19,580
even if His Majesty punishes me.

259
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:37,740
What are you looking for?

260
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,620
I have two more jars.

261
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:44,340
I’ll ask a maid to get them.

262
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:46,980
Being drunk is harmful to health.

263
00:14:47,860 --> 00:14:48,940
Liaozi asked the maids

264
00:14:48,940 --> 00:14:49,900
to make some hangover-cure soup.

265
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:55,300
I’m not drunk.

266
00:14:57,220 --> 00:14:58,700
I’m never drunk.

267
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:05,100
You didn’t behave like this.

268
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:12,580
Am I...

269
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:14,060
Am I disgracing myself?

270
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:16,580
I don’t think so.

271
00:15:21,020 --> 00:15:22,500
You’re in your husband’s room,

272
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:23,940
why are you afraid of disgracing yourself?

273
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:30,260
Danshu.

274
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:33,980
Even when you’re disgraced,

275
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:34,980
it won’t be screwed.

276
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:41,340
On the day of coup,

277
00:15:42,540 --> 00:15:43,700
you struggled not to

278
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:45,940
disgrace yourself.

279
00:15:48,060 --> 00:15:49,060
But in fact,

280
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:52,540
were you really that calm?

281
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:54,580
Were you not scared

282
00:15:55,460 --> 00:15:56,300
or worried?

283
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:14,860
Are you blaming me

284
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:16,900
for punishing Ling’er?

285
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:22,860
Do you really think

286
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:25,820
she must be killed?

287
00:16:41,780 --> 00:16:43,660
I just wanted to get rid of it,

288
00:16:45,900 --> 00:16:47,100
in case of getting involved.

289
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:54,860
A mere maid.

290
00:16:58,380 --> 00:16:59,740
A mere maid.

291
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,420
But did you really get rid of it?

292
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:05,220
Do you know

293
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:08,180
Yang Huaimin’s killing

294
00:17:09,620 --> 00:17:11,620
the last treasonous guard

295
00:17:12,140 --> 00:17:14,660
against my rule

296
00:17:15,020 --> 00:17:16,060
and the Empress’s killing a maid

297
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:17,460
who had fornication with a guard

298
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:19,900
were mentioned in the same breath?

299
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:20,780
Both of you are considered
as destroying the evidence.

300
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,540
Your Majesty, if you want to investigate it,

301
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:45,780
interrogate me,

302
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:47,180
ground me,

303
00:17:47,980 --> 00:17:49,220
or imprison me,

304
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,100
I won’t complain.

305
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:56,180
Can’t you listen to me once?

306
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:57,900
It’s been over ten years.

307
00:17:58,180 --> 00:18:00,340
When we argue, you always say

308
00:18:00,340 --> 00:18:01,940
“Punish me, Your Majesty”.

309
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:11,780
When you say you’re sorry

310
00:18:11,780 --> 00:18:12,540
and you’re wrong,

311
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:13,420
do you really think

312
00:18:13,420 --> 00:18:14,620
you’re wrong?

313
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:17,180
When you say you’re wrong,

314
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:19,500
you mean I’m muddleheaded.

315
00:18:32,540 --> 00:18:33,860
I’m wrong, Your Majesty.

316
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:39,580
I’m absolutely wrong.

317
00:18:42,860 --> 00:18:46,940
I’m merciless and stupid.

318
00:18:51,420 --> 00:18:53,860
I didn’t show any mercy,

319
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:58,780
and there’s more trouble now.

320
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:04,420
You don’t need to humiliate me.

321
00:19:08,260 --> 00:19:09,220
Why don’t you repudiate me?

322
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:11,900
Cao Danshu.

323
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:13,420
It’s so stupid of you!

324
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:16,500
Do you think any man

325
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:19,140
wants to marry a living Buddha?

326
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:34,580
I didn’t know

327
00:19:36,100 --> 00:19:37,660
what Ling’er would get you involved in.

328
00:19:39,100 --> 00:19:40,980
She really did capital offence.

329
00:19:43,060 --> 00:19:43,860
Well...

330
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:46,620
you weren’t merciful enough

331
00:19:46,620 --> 00:19:47,740
and you weren’t wise enough.

332
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:49,140
So, there is trouble now.

333
00:19:54,900 --> 00:19:56,740
But who doesn’t make mistakes?

334
00:19:59,980 --> 00:20:01,380
I made a lot of mistakes

335
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:03,540
didn’t I?

336
00:20:07,860 --> 00:20:09,700
When I was self-willed at a young age

337
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,660
and quarreled with Empress Dowager,

338
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:15,140
I accidentally got a common family

339
00:20:15,140 --> 00:20:17,060
lose their lives.

340
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:20,860
In Haoshuichuan Battle, I misjudged

341
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:22,340
and supported Han Qi’s rash advance.

342
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:24,340
Over ten thousand soldiers

343
00:20:25,540 --> 00:20:26,780
lost their lives.

344
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:32,100
Your Majesty.

345
00:20:33,900 --> 00:20:35,340
Don’t always

346
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:36,500
blame yourself.

347
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:41,460
I asked the physicians.

348
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,780
You always have the heart disease,

349
00:20:45,860 --> 00:20:48,060
mainly because you’re too anxious.

350
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:05,900
Stand up.

351
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:14,380
Danshu.

352
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:16,260
You’re a subordinate.

353
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:18,820
But you’re also my wife.

354
00:21:21,140 --> 00:21:22,860
When you’re in trouble

355
00:21:22,860 --> 00:21:23,980
or make a mistake,

356
00:21:25,980 --> 00:21:27,980
as long as you aren’t against rules or laws,

357
00:21:30,180 --> 00:21:31,100
don’t always try to

358
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:33,140
argue with the Emperor

359
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:35,140
or ask for punishment.

360
00:21:36,020 --> 00:21:37,900
You still have your husband to share with you,

361
00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:40,260
defend you or mend for you.

362
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:04,260
You’re funny.

363
00:22:05,580 --> 00:22:07,380
You’re an evil official.

364
00:22:08,020 --> 00:22:09,620
You’re supposed to be sensual and greedy

365
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,300
who drink and enjoy

366
00:22:11,300 --> 00:22:13,020
with your concubines every day.

367
00:22:13,820 --> 00:22:15,020
But look at you.

368
00:22:16,020 --> 00:22:16,980
You exchanged

369
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:18,700
all the treasures

370
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:19,980
into these metal scraps,

371
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:21,060
bamboo slices

372
00:22:21,060 --> 00:22:21,900
and tortoise shells.

373
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:23,620
And for those women,

374
00:22:24,900 --> 00:22:25,860
they used to

375
00:22:25,860 --> 00:22:27,500
live a poor life in theatres.

376
00:22:28,620 --> 00:22:29,620
But after they came here,

377
00:22:30,820 --> 00:22:32,180
they’re enjoying themselves.

378
00:22:35,980 --> 00:22:38,540
I hate saints the most.

379
00:22:39,820 --> 00:22:40,780
I especially hate

380
00:22:40,780 --> 00:22:42,380
those guys who claim to be kindhearted.

381
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:46,260
Fan Zhongyan and Ouyang Xiu

382
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,220
can dismiss redundant officials,

383
00:22:48,220 --> 00:22:50,220
but they always threaten with the benevolence.

384
00:22:50,260 --> 00:22:51,500
That’s disgusting!

385
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:54,060
Yulan.

386
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,540
Do you know

387
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:56,820
why I like such antiques?

388
00:22:59,660 --> 00:23:01,420
You liked them since you were little, didn’t you?

389
00:23:02,620 --> 00:23:04,060
You didn’t have enough money then,

390
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:06,420
and you swindled everywhere.

391
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:13,500
Since I turned nineteen,

392
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:14,780
I never believed

393
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:16,620
Yao, Shun and Yu were perfect emperors

394
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:18,380
or Duke of Zhou was a perfect man.

395
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:22,780
I wanted to find such antiques

396
00:23:22,860 --> 00:23:25,620
and read the characters on them

397
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:28,940
so that I can see

398
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:31,780
if perfect emperors also manipulated power

399
00:23:31,780 --> 00:23:32,860
and were self-willed

400
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:35,460
and if Duke of Zhou

401
00:23:35,460 --> 00:23:36,820
was also greedy and sensual

402
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:38,780
just like me.

403
00:23:44,020 --> 00:23:46,620
Have you found any evidence?

404
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:54,660
It’s hard to find antiques.

405
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:57,860
It’s also hard to read ancient characters.

406
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:03,620
I haven’t found any evidence

407
00:24:03,620 --> 00:24:04,940
on imperfect saints.

408
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:08,300
But from a word or two,

409
00:24:08,300 --> 00:24:09,460
I see that

410
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:12,140
scriptures passed down by scholars

411
00:24:12,660 --> 00:24:14,060
may not be real.

412
00:24:15,700 --> 00:24:16,620
Interesting.

413
00:24:16,900 --> 00:24:18,580
Quite interesting!

414
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:29,980
In the revolt of Qinghe County,

415
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:33,060
Ming Hao failed to break into the town.

416
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:35,700
Scholar Wen, you went there to fight.

417
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:36,780
In less than two months,

418
00:24:36,780 --> 00:24:38,180
you broke in and killed the traitors.

419
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:40,940
You even gave right rewards and punishments.

420
00:24:40,940 --> 00:24:41,900
You placated common people,

421
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:42,980
banned the cult

422
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:46,500
and allowed local people to borrow money for seeds

423
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:47,540
in case of missing the farming season.

424
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:50,220
You’ve made great contributions.

425
00:24:55,580 --> 00:24:57,020
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =
I took down the town,

426
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,380
with the blessing of Your Majesty

427
00:24:58,380 --> 00:24:59,300
and the help of brave generals.

428
00:24:59,860 --> 00:25:01,380
Before I left,

429
00:25:01,380 --> 00:25:02,300
you taught me how to

430
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,260
ban the cult and instruct people

431
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:05,220
so that I knew

432
00:25:05,220 --> 00:25:06,420
I should treat the cult members

433
00:25:06,420 --> 00:25:07,380
as ignorant common people,

434
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:09,380
instead of traitors.

435
00:25:10,740 --> 00:25:12,460
It’s kind and farsighted of you, Your Majesty.

436
00:25:12,580 --> 00:25:14,300
I really admire that.

437
00:25:15,780 --> 00:25:16,940
Don’t be modest.

438
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:18,660
I’m not.

439
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:20,340
Deputy Military Governor Ming Hao

440
00:25:20,340 --> 00:25:21,380
failed to take down the town,

441
00:25:21,620 --> 00:25:23,460
only because most of his proposals

442
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:24,220
were held back

443
00:25:24,220 --> 00:25:25,620
by Xia Song.

444
00:25:25,620 --> 00:25:26,820
And the war was delayed.

445
00:25:28,580 --> 00:25:30,340
I have something to say, Your Majesty.

446
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:34,580
Scholar Wen was modest.

447
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:37,420
= Chen Zhizhong, courtesy name Zhaoyu =
But he was telling the truth

448
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:39,540
that Xia Song interfered

449
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:40,820
with the battle.

450
00:25:41,460 --> 00:25:43,460
Xia Song is always jealous of virtuous officials

451
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:44,460
and gets rid of dissidents.

452
00:25:44,780 --> 00:25:47,740
In the coup, he sheltered Yang Huaimin

453
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:49,580
and framed Her Highness up.

454
00:25:49,820 --> 00:25:51,060
Haven’t I already

455
00:25:51,060 --> 00:25:52,220
approved of your proposals

456
00:25:52,260 --> 00:25:54,300
and banished Yang Huaimin from the Capital?

457
00:25:56,180 --> 00:25:56,900
I don’t think

458
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:59,100
= He Tan, courtesy name Shengcong =
banishing Yang Huaimin is enough.

459
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:01,780
Blaming Xia Song is the right way.

460
00:26:02,780 --> 00:26:05,500
Yang Huaimin often colluded with Xia Song.

461
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:09,340
Xia Song isn’t a good man.

462
00:26:09,660 --> 00:26:11,020
He’s greedy and extravagant.

463
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:12,500
Your Majesty,

464
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,460
he is good at

465
00:26:13,460 --> 00:26:14,860
flattering you.

466
00:26:15,380 --> 00:26:16,780
But he never does his duty

467
00:26:16,860 --> 00:26:18,300
to give honest advice.

468
00:26:28,820 --> 00:26:30,100
I was absent-minded.

469
00:26:30,260 --> 00:26:32,660
I didn’t hear what you said.

470
00:26:34,820 --> 00:26:35,740
The other day,

471
00:26:36,420 --> 00:26:39,500
the Empress and I took Princess Fukang

472
00:26:39,660 --> 00:26:41,300
and some madams to the temple.

473
00:26:41,780 --> 00:26:42,900
We stopped on the way,

474
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:45,580
to buy some osmanthus cakes

475
00:26:45,580 --> 00:26:46,740
and pine nut candies.

476
00:26:47,340 --> 00:26:48,780
The wrapping paper

477
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:50,180
is the tabloid of the Capital.

478
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:52,180
Princess Fukang read it curiously

479
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:54,300
and told me that

480
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:56,220
it was about officials,

481
00:26:57,300 --> 00:27:01,220
but its writing is better than the court bulletins’

482
00:27:01,900 --> 00:27:02,940
from Bureau of Reports.

483
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,140
Since Su Shunqin and Wang Yirou

484
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:13,100
were demoted and banished.

485
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,460
Bureau of Reports lacks talents.

486
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:17,780
And the reports are more vulgar.

487
00:27:18,300 --> 00:27:19,220
I think

488
00:27:19,420 --> 00:27:22,460
Su Shunqin and the other were unrestrained,

489
00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:24,340
disgracing scholars.

490
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:25,740
You punished them right, Your Majesty.

491
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:28,660
But they weren’t rebellious

492
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:30,100
or corrupt.

493
00:27:30,180 --> 00:27:31,580
They just made an indiscreet remark.

494
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:34,060
It’s been three years since they were banished.

495
00:27:34,540 --> 00:27:35,860
In their poems and letters,

496
00:27:35,860 --> 00:27:37,020
they have regretted.

497
00:27:37,220 --> 00:27:39,460
And they don’t write as wildly as they used to.

498
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:40,660
I think

499
00:27:40,740 --> 00:27:41,940
it’s a pity

500
00:27:42,140 --> 00:27:44,180
if a talent like Su Shunqin

501
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:46,220
can’t work for the imperial court.

502
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,060
What do you think, Scholar Wen?

503
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:57,180
I think

504
00:27:58,540 --> 00:28:00,500
He Tan makes sense.

505
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:05,300
I think so.

506
00:28:06,620 --> 00:28:07,420
How about...

507
00:28:11,060 --> 00:28:12,460
How about discussing about

508
00:28:12,940 --> 00:28:14,500
reinstating Su Shunqin

509
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:17,420
as the adjutant of Huzhou?

510
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:22,260
I was speaking of Xia Song.

511
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:24,380
But His Majesty...

512
00:28:25,300 --> 00:28:26,940
He was digressing.

513
00:28:28,020 --> 00:28:29,220
When he mentioned Zimei,

514
00:28:29,900 --> 00:28:31,140
I forgot about

515
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:32,700
Xia Song’s problem.

516
00:28:35,180 --> 00:28:37,340
Zimei was truly unlucky.

517
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,020
Wang Gongchen was so stubborn

518
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:40,100
and he totally fired Zimei.

519
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:42,260
That was heavy punishment.

520
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:44,420
But now he’s back to work.

521
00:28:44,500 --> 00:28:45,980
It means His Majesty has cooled down.

522
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,140
That’s great.

523
00:28:48,100 --> 00:28:49,900
As for Xia Song,

524
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:51,660
don’t rush.

525
00:28:52,300 --> 00:28:53,500
How can I not rush?

526
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:56,020
Xia Song is such an evil guy!

527
00:28:57,500 --> 00:28:59,900
He was ruthless to Shi Jie.

528
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:01,620
And for Su Zimei,

529
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:03,700
Wang Gongchen apparently

530
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:04,580
didn’t let go of him.

531
00:29:04,740 --> 00:29:06,180
But didn’t Xia Song

532
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:07,580
stir up trouble secretly?

533
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:10,860
Xia Song never likes any honest official.

534
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:12,780
In this case,

535
00:29:12,780 --> 00:29:13,860
when His Majesty

536
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:16,420
reinstated Su Zimei,

537
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:19,340
could he mean something else?

538
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,300
You really are sick?

539
00:29:34,460 --> 00:29:35,500
Leave us. Let me do it.

540
00:29:42,460 --> 00:29:43,580
What’s wrong with you?

541
00:29:45,140 --> 00:29:46,500
You think I pretend to be ill

542
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:49,060
and you still come to see me?

543
00:29:51,260 --> 00:29:53,220
I come out to take a message

544
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,780
to Wang Gongchen’s wife and Wang Zhi’s wife

545
00:29:55,060 --> 00:29:56,580
and check on you on my way.

546
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:02,820
Tell me.

547
00:30:03,740 --> 00:30:04,980
Why is Madam Zhang

548
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:07,780
struggling for promotion?

549
00:30:09,780 --> 00:30:11,180
She has realized that

550
00:30:11,980 --> 00:30:13,100
without a status,

551
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:14,180
no love

552
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:15,460
can last long.

553
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:18,860
I heard

554
00:30:19,380 --> 00:30:21,100
Wang Zhi and the other

555
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:22,620
advised His Majesty to promote Madam Zhang.

556
00:30:24,620 --> 00:30:26,860
His Majesty also told some officials that

557
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:27,860
on the night of coup,

558
00:30:28,020 --> 00:30:29,140
Madam Zhang rushed out

559
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:30,620
and protected him.

560
00:30:37,340 --> 00:30:38,940
If Lantiao can have a son

561
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:40,300
and he can be raised up by Madam Zhang...

562
00:30:40,820 --> 00:30:43,300
His Majesty doesn’t like the Empress.

563
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:45,660
By then, you can report that

564
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:50,020
a maid of the Empress has fornication with a guard.

565
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:53,300
If rumor goes out that

566
00:30:53,740 --> 00:30:54,660
Her Highness’s favorite maid Qiuhe

567
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,380
had a relationship with Imperial Artist Cui Bai.

568
00:30:57,300 --> 00:30:59,820
Maybe, our plan will work.

569
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:03,380
But Yang Huaimin

570
00:31:03,420 --> 00:31:06,100
was already banished.

571
00:31:07,860 --> 00:31:09,220
Imperial Security Agency

572
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:11,580
is under the control of Zhang Maoze again.

573
00:31:12,820 --> 00:31:14,980
This is due to those censors.

574
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:16,820
It’s okay.

575
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,980
He’ll be back in a couple of days.

576
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:23,540
Back in a couple of days?

577
00:31:27,340 --> 00:31:28,980
You never know.

578
00:31:30,220 --> 00:31:33,020
Wen Yanbo seldom discusses much.

579
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:36,660
His wife is close to Madam Zhang.

580
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:39,580
He is on good terms with

581
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:40,500
Madam Zhang’s uncle.

582
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:42,100
Yeah.

583
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:43,020
What’s wrong?

584
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:46,540
Nothing.

585
00:31:46,660 --> 00:31:47,620
I just didn’t expect that

586
00:31:47,620 --> 00:31:49,660
the revolt in Qinghe County was put down so soon.

587
00:31:50,420 --> 00:31:51,780
When Wen Yanbo broke in town,

588
00:31:52,860 --> 00:31:53,780
he

589
00:31:53,780 --> 00:31:55,860
placated the cult.

590
00:31:56,380 --> 00:31:58,620
He only executed some heads of the cult.

591
00:31:59,140 --> 00:32:01,100
He ran official schools to destroy the cult.

592
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:04,180
And he didn’t even treat followers of cult

593
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:05,740
throughout the country as traitors

594
00:32:05,740 --> 00:32:08,300
because of the revolt.

595
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:13,100
What does that concern us?

596
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:14,860
Anyway,

597
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:16,940
he won’t object to the promotion of Madam Zhang.

598
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:21,420
Cult followers weren’t tracked down

599
00:32:21,660 --> 00:32:23,380
in or out of the imperial court.

600
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:26,980
His Majesty even let go of the coup

601
00:32:26,980 --> 00:32:28,060
in the imperial court.

602
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:29,740
I don’t know where to start the plan.

603
00:32:34,660 --> 00:32:35,660
All right.

604
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:36,980
See?

605
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:39,340
I bought you a pair of

606
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:41,020
opal earrings.

607
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:43,020
Do you like them?

608
00:32:44,420 --> 00:32:45,140
No.

609
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:50,140
Looking forward to your next visit.

610
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:50,736
All right.

611
00:32:50,763 --> 00:32:53,506
Go. Go. Okay. Okay.

612
00:33:04,563 --> 00:33:05,706
Excuse me. Step aside.

613
00:33:12,020 --> 00:33:13,460
It’s been only two months.

614
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:15,620
Seems like

615
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:18,140
you’ve sold all the old goods out.

616
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,420
I sold them out yesterday.

617
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:21,860
I sold the last ones

618
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:23,620
to Khitan merchants.

619
00:33:23,820 --> 00:33:24,620
Did you?

620
00:33:25,420 --> 00:33:26,540
Now,

621
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:28,220
the fashion of silks and brocades

622
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:30,020
changes quickly.

623
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:31,940
Girls of our nation

624
00:33:32,020 --> 00:33:33,460
are picky.

625
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:36,060
I won’t sell old-fashioned styles to them.

626
00:33:36,940 --> 00:33:38,020
I have to sell them

627
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:39,420
to Khitan people.

628
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:40,980
The worst goods

629
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:43,740
can only be sold to Xizangs, Xixia people

630
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:44,820
or Cantonese.

631
00:33:45,860 --> 00:33:47,740
Double-color silk from the south

632
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:49,860
and camel hair blankets from Uighur.

633
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:51,780
I only keep them for you.

634
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:53,380
Double-color silk?

635
00:33:53,780 --> 00:33:54,660
Which do you mean?

636
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:02,780
These two look similar.

637
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:04,500
And they both look good.

638
00:34:05,100 --> 00:34:05,940
Well,

639
00:34:05,940 --> 00:34:07,060
pack these two

640
00:34:07,220 --> 00:34:08,500
and send them to my place.

641
00:34:08,660 --> 00:34:09,220
Okay.

642
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:10,220
I’m sure

643
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:11,380
Madam Zhang will like them.

644
00:34:11,500 --> 00:34:12,420
Okay. Okay.

645
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:13,580
All right. Thank you.

646
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:16,900
Last night,

647
00:34:17,020 --> 00:34:18,820
you said in the routine inspection,

648
00:34:19,060 --> 00:34:20,700
you found him carry a tea cup

649
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:21,900
and a silver cup

650
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:22,820
without any record.

651
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:25,180
= Zhang Chengzhao =
And he failed to explain where he got them.

652
00:34:25,540 --> 00:34:26,580
You sent him to us, then.

653
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,420
We searched his room immediately

654
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:30,300
and found these, including

655
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:34,340
powder of five minerals and aphrodisiac.

656
00:34:39,180 --> 00:34:40,660
You didn’t alert anyone, did you?

657
00:34:41,220 --> 00:34:42,340
You told us to keep a low profile.

658
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:43,500
We were very cautious.

659
00:34:44,140 --> 00:34:45,020
We confirmed

660
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:46,260
no one was in his yard.

661
00:35:02,140 --> 00:35:03,660
Do you want to confess

662
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:06,260
and get a chance to make amends?

663
00:35:07,380 --> 00:35:09,980
Or do you want me to ask physicians

664
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:12,020
to check these prescriptions

665
00:35:12,940 --> 00:35:14,060
and see what dirty things

666
00:35:14,500 --> 00:35:16,580
you have brought into

667
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:18,180
the Pavilion of Luan?

668
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:24,580
And these treasures.

669
00:35:25,220 --> 00:35:27,660
Will you tell me honestly

670
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:29,380
where you got them

671
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:31,180
and why you got them?

672
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:33,460
Or shall I

673
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:36,180
give them to Officer Ren

674
00:35:36,740 --> 00:35:37,940
and let him check up on them?

675
00:35:40,700 --> 00:35:41,460
Mr. Zhang.

676
00:35:48,620 --> 00:35:49,380
Mr. Zhang.

677
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:52,260
I’ll confess.

678
00:35:53,220 --> 00:35:54,180
I’ll confess.

679
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:57,500
I’d like to atone for my crimes.

680
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:05,820
Go get my pickled plums

681
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:06,860
and haws.

682
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:09,980
Your Majesty, you’re coughing lately.

683
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:11,980
The plums and haws

684
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:14,140
were boiled.

685
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:15,180
Drink it after meals

686
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:16,860
and it stops coughing and helps digestion.

687
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:17,980
Huirou and I tried it.

688
00:36:19,780 --> 00:36:21,020
You always know how to keep in good health.

689
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:23,140
You haven’t changed much in the last ten years.

690
00:36:23,740 --> 00:36:25,620
What are you talking about?

691
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:28,340
You always know how to make me happy.

692
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:31,140
Huirou is even engaged.

693
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:34,980
Huirou.

694
00:36:35,980 --> 00:36:36,860
What are you thinking of?

695
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:41,980
Father.

696
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:47,220
I’ve been reading

697
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:48,340
Tao Yuanming’s poems.

698
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:49,380
I love them.

699
00:36:52,700 --> 00:36:54,220
You like Tao Yuanming?

700
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:56,420
That’s great.

701
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:58,140
What have you read?

702
00:36:58,220 --> 00:36:59,300
Which are your favorites?

703
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:02,300
The Story of Five-willow Gentleman,

704
00:37:02,300 --> 00:37:03,620
Ah, Homeward Bound I go!

705
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:05,540
Thirty Poems on the Classic of Mountains and Seas

706
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:10,540
and Ode to Leisure.

707
00:37:19,260 --> 00:37:20,540
Which parts do you like the most?

708
00:37:21,180 --> 00:37:23,020
Recite some to me.

709
00:37:26,780 --> 00:37:29,700
I like...

710
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:33,660
I read them from time to time.

711
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:35,500
I don’t know

712
00:37:35,740 --> 00:37:37,300
if I understand them correctly.

713
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:40,100
Father.

714
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:44,100
What?

715
00:37:45,700 --> 00:37:47,220
You want me to explain to you?

716
00:37:47,900 --> 00:37:49,020
No. No. No.

717
00:37:50,380 --> 00:37:51,460
Father, you work so hard.

718
00:37:51,700 --> 00:37:53,220
You’ve got so many things to do.

719
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:55,100
It’s a little problem.

720
00:37:55,660 --> 00:37:57,900
Why don’t you let Huaiji

721
00:37:58,060 --> 00:37:59,140
explain to me?

722
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:05,620
Fine, then.

723
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:07,380
I’ve got some

724
00:38:07,420 --> 00:38:08,420
important proposals to review.

725
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:11,460
I’m going back.

726
00:38:26,620 --> 00:38:27,700
You’ve made up your mind?

727
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:32,060
Yes. Yes.

728
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:34,220
Uh...

729
00:38:35,340 --> 00:38:36,460
Let me calm down.

730
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:40,100
Let me calm down.

731
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,900
That’ll be fine.

732
00:38:44,780 --> 00:38:47,100
Be careful when you talk to Lantiao.

733
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:48,740
Don’t let her see you through.

734
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:51,180
Aye. Aye.

735
00:38:51,740 --> 00:38:52,740
Wait here.

736
00:38:53,140 --> 00:38:53,740
Aye.

737
00:39:34,140 --> 00:39:36,900
I wish I could be the collar of her blouse

738
00:39:38,220 --> 00:39:40,860
so that I would smell her.

739
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:45,260
What a pity that she takes off her blouse at night!

740
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:49,900
I hate it when the day doesn’t break yet.

741
00:39:52,580 --> 00:39:55,180
I wish I could be the belt of her dress

742
00:39:57,220 --> 00:40:01,100
so that I would cover her body.

743
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:06,220
What a pity that the weather changes!

744
00:40:07,980 --> 00:40:11,020
She will put on new dresses.

745
00:40:13,580 --> 00:40:17,300
I wish I could be the pomade on her hair

746
00:40:18,980 --> 00:40:22,420
so that I would smooth her hair.

747
00:40:24,340 --> 00:40:27,060
What a pity that she takes showers!

748
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:34,540
I must suffer in the hot water.

749
00:40:36,780 --> 00:40:40,820
I wish I could be the makeup on her eye brows,

750
00:40:43,340 --> 00:40:47,460
so that I could shine when she looks around.

751
00:40:55,900 --> 00:40:56,580
Princess.

752
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:00,580
What?

753
00:41:03,540 --> 00:41:05,980
Which sentence don’t you understand?

754
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:09,060
How could I not understand?

755
00:41:09,380 --> 00:41:10,340
I understand every sentence.

756
00:41:11,100 --> 00:41:11,940
But...

757
00:41:12,180 --> 00:41:14,100
I asked father to leave you to me

758
00:41:14,500 --> 00:41:15,860
and read Ode to Leisure with me

759
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:17,740
from the very beginning.

760
00:41:22,460 --> 00:41:23,220
Huaiji.

761
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:25,420
Do you think

762
00:41:27,180 --> 00:41:28,820
Tao Yuanming is handsome?

763
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:33,460
A romantic celebrity like him

764
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:36,860
always makes people admire him.

765
00:41:39,260 --> 00:41:40,260
So...

766
00:41:41,620 --> 00:41:43,540
could he be as handsome as Cao?

767
00:41:49,100 --> 00:41:49,860
Huaiji.

768
00:41:50,580 --> 00:41:51,340
Look.

769
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:53,580
Cao gave me this

770
00:41:53,700 --> 00:41:54,980
