771
00:41:55,900 --> 00:41:57,220
Together with the jade comb.

772
00:42:03,460 --> 00:42:07,220
I wish I could be the pomade on her hair

773
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:12,060
so that I would smooth her hair.

774
00:42:16,100 --> 00:42:17,580
When she said Ode to Leisure,

775
00:42:17,580 --> 00:42:18,580
and I noticed her look,

776
00:42:18,580 --> 00:42:19,620
I knew something must be wrong.

777
00:42:20,500 --> 00:42:22,260
I’m right! I’m right!

778
00:42:22,300 --> 00:42:23,060
You...

779
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:25,700
If I didn’t ask you,

780
00:42:25,700 --> 00:42:26,900
